クラス Timewindow

  • java.lang.Object
    • manhattan.timewindow.Timewindow

    public class Timewindow
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Timewindow>
    Time window starting and ending time.
    Those are round off to the 3rd decimal place.

    This class is IMMUTABLE

    バージョン:
    0.1.0
    作成者:
    Kensuke
